h talent\", \"from\": 806, \"to\": 836}, {\"ngram\": \"the Covid-19 lockdown\", \"from\": 910, \"to\": 931}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Bell, who in a fairy-tale twist was also born in Paris, said: \\\"I have had so many nice messages from people, be them athletes or just parents or whatever saying, 'You have inspired me to get back into an old sport or an old hobby'.\", \"from\": 934, \"to\": 1165, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 983, \"end\": 988, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.5974744748500497e-14, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Bell\", \"from\": 934, \"to\": 938}, {\"ngram\": \"a fairy-tale twist\", \"from\": 947, \"to\": 965}, {\"ngram\": \"so many nice messages\", \"from\": 1008, \"to\": 1029}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 1035, \"to\": 1041}, {\"ngram\": \"them athletes\", \"from\": 1046, \"to\": 1059}, {\"ngram\": \"just parents\", \"from\": 1063, \"to\": 1075}, {\"ngram\": \"whatever\", \"from\": 1079, \"to\": 1087}, {\"ngram\": \"an old sport\", \"from\": 1135, \"to\": 1147}, {\"ngram\": \"an old hobby\", \"from\": 1151, \"to\": 1163}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"When I got back into it, the goal wasn't to make the Olympics, that would have seemed kind of bonkers at the time.\", \"from\": 1167, \"to\": 1282, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the goal\", \"from\": 1193, \"to\": 1201}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1217, \"to\": 1229}, {\"ngram\": \"bonkers\", \"from\": 1262, \"to\": 1269}, {\"ngram\": \"the time\", \"from\": 1273, \"to\": 1281}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But just keep going.\", \"from\": 1283, \"to\": 1303, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's never too late to go back to something that you enjoy.\", \"from\": 1305, \"to\": 1365, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 1340, \"to\": 1349}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am a happy athlete and I think anyone can take away from that, there is no set path.\", \"from\": 1366, \"to\": 1452, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a happy athlete\", \"from\": 1371, \"to\": 1386}, {\"ngram\": \"anyone\", \"from\": 1399, \"to\": 1405}, {\"ngram\": \"no set path\", \"from\": 1440, \"to\": 1451}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Mine's a very unconventional route.\\\"\", \"from\": 1453, \"to\": 1489, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Mine\", \"from\": 1453, \"to\": 1457}, {\"ngram\": \"a very unconventional route\", \"from\": 1460, \"to\": 1487}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Kenya's Faith Kipyegon lowered the Olympic record to 3:51.29 to claim gold and defend her title for a second time, while Australia's Jessica Hull took silver, 0.05 seconds faster than Bell's new British record of 3:52.61.\", \"from\": 1491, \"to\": 1712, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1491, \"end\": 1496, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenya\", \"score\": 0.9991753168718427, \"rank\": 0.0008253283045767413, \"text\": \"Kenya\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenya\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenya\"}, {\"begin\": 1499, \"end\": 1513, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Faith_Kipyegon\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Faith Kipyegon\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Faith_Kipyegon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Faith_Kipyegon\"}, {\"begin\": 1612, \"end\": 1621, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_cricket_team\", \"score\": 0.9970393185643254, \"rank\": 0.0023147540768487162, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_cricket_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_cricket_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1624, \"end\": 1636, \"title\": \"htt