"from\": 3003, \"to\": 3013}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She started with a few parkruns and was pleasantly surprised she still had the speed, so she rang up old coach Trevor Painter, who alongside Jenny Meadows also trains newly-crowned 800m champion Keely Hodgkinson, and started taking the sport seriously again.\", \"from\": 3016, \"to\": 3274, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3157, \"end\": 3170, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jenny_Meadows\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jenny Meadows\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jenny_Meadows\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jenny_Meadows\"}, {\"begin\": 3211, \"end\": 3227, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keely_Hodgkinson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Keely Hodgkinson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keely_Hodgkinson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keely_Hodgkinson\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a few parkruns\", \"from\": 3033, \"to\": 3047}, {\"ngram\": \"the speed\", \"from\": 3091, \"to\": 3100}, {\"ngram\": \"old coach Trevor Painter\", \"from\": 3117, \"to\": 3141}, {\"ngram\": \"newly-crowned 800m champion\", \"from\": 3183, \"to\": 3210}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 3248, \"to\": 3257}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As recently as May, Bell was still working a nine-to-five job in cybersecurity sales and a month later was crowned 1500m champion at the British Olympic trials to book her place in Paris.\", \"from\": 3276, \"to\": 3463, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3413, \"end\": 3420, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\", \"score\": 0.9910061376364738, \"rank\": 0.007898681663696193, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q23442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\"}, {\"begin\": 3457, \"end\": 3462, \"title\": \"http://dbp